From 453e8d5fcc6b1c21bb6cd83a3cabf9695f2fd6b8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Salman Wahib <sxlmnwb.dev@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 20:56:49 +0700
Subject: [PATCH] sched: add BORE Scheduler v5.9.6 for android15-6.6

Burst-Oriented Response Enhancer (BORE) scheduler improves interactivity
by tracking burst behavior per-task and adjusting vruntime penalties accordingly.

Source: https://github.com/sxlmnwb/bore-scheduler-android
Patch: 0001-android15-6.6-bore-5.9.6.patch

Tested Kernel Source: https://android.googlesource.com/kernel/common
Branch: android15-6.6-2026-04

Tested-by: Salman Wahib <sxlmnwb.dev@gmail.com>
Co-authored-by: Masahito S <firelzrd@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: Salman Wahib <sxlmnwb.dev@gmail.com>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/gki_defconfig |   4 +
 include/linux/sched.h            |  13 +-
 include/linux/sched/bore.h       |  53 ++++
 init/Kconfig                     |  17 ++
 kernel/Kconfig.hz                |  17 ++
 kernel/fork.c                    |  20 ++
 kernel/sched/Makefile            |   1 +
 kernel/sched/bore.c              | 466 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 kernel/sched/core.c              |   6 +
 kernel/sched/debug.c             |  66 ++++-
 kernel/sched/fair.c              | 100 ++++++-
 kernel/sched/features.h          |   4 +
 kernel/sched/sched.h             |  10 +
 13 files changed, 771 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 include/linux/sched/bore.h
 create mode 100644 kernel/sched/bore.c

